<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .error-container h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .error-container p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .error-details {
            background: #ffebee;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .error-list {
            text-align: left;
            color: #c62828;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .error-list li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .retry-btn {
            background: #4285f4;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .retry-btn:hover {
            background: #357ae8;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .home-btn {
            background: #6c757d;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .home-btn:hover {
            background: #5a6268;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer-info {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">üö´</div>
        <h1>Login Failed</h1>
        <p>We encountered an error while trying to sign you in with Google. This could be due to several reasons.</p>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <strong>Possible causes:</strong>
            <ul class="error-list">
                <li>üî∏ Authentication was cancelled or denied</li>
                <li>üî∏ Network connectivity issues</li>
                <li>üî∏ Google OAuth service temporary unavailability</li>
                <li>üî∏ Invalid OAuth configuration</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="/auth/google" class="retry-btn">
                üîÑ Try Again
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="home-btn">
                üè† Go Home
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-info">
            <p>If the problem persists, please contact support.</p>
            <p>Edit Code Editor - by nitinrajput16</p>
            <p>Time: <%= new Date().toLocaleString('en-IN', { timeZone: 'Asia/Kolkata' }) %> IST</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>